    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Drive Thru 是一款第一人称视角的模拟游戏，在游戏中玩家将直接与顾客互动，接受他们的订单，在厨房准备食物和饮料，并处理付款事宜。您的目标是通过战略决策吸引更多顾客，提高餐厅效率，从而提升顾客满意度，促进业务增长。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/412e1297fba0e44aa9534758b1ed6d40.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/412e1297fba0e44aa9534758b1ed6d40.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/412e1297fba0e44aa9534758b1ed6d40.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍟<strong> 主要特点：</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在线购物时间！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >订购您需要的一切，确保您的餐厅顺利运营！新鲜的食材、必需的用品和厨房升级——一切都直接送到您家门口。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/5ec009d540dc8a90c110d7e472cc929e.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/5ec009d540dc8a90c110d7e472cc929e.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/5ec009d540dc8a90c110d7e472cc929e.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快速配送，新鲜食材！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持高质量的农产品、肉类和必需品的库存。良好的库存管理意味着更满意的顾客和更快速的服务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/d1a9331b9951bc39e28f0f52b103c278.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/d1a9331b9951bc39e28f0f52b103c278.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/d1a9331b9951bc39e28f0f52b103c278.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>补充库存与整理！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过正确安排食材来高效管理存储空间。保持厨房充足的库存，避免在高峰时段缺少关键物品！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/d49c6e20b225b4162d5f78c3ec2a3bd8.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/d49c6e20b225b4162d5f78c3ec2a3bd8.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/d49c6e20b225b4162d5f78c3ec2a3bd8.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随意摆放！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义您的餐厅布局！根据您的需求，精准地安置烹饪站、准备区域和储藏区，确保工作流的最高效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/8e23387cd8e700174a15ac29e0337da9.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/8e23387cd8e700174a15ac29e0337da9.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/8e23387cd8e700174a15ac29e0337da9.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为烤炉大师！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烤制多汁的汉堡，炸出脆皮薯条，精确地烹饪美味的餐点。完美您的烹饪技巧，提供城里最好的快餐！ <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/1c6035fec18d66609852833e94695749.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/1c6035fec18d66609852833e94695749.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/1c6035fec18d66609852833e94695749.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>清洁时间！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持厨房和就餐区一尘不染，以确保获得最高的卫生评级。干净的餐厅意味着更好的评论和更满意的顾客！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/63df13e452218eea021f429112e63e96.poster.avif?t=1768213542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/63df13e452218eea021f429112e63e96.webm?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062060/extras/63df13e452218eea021f429112e63e96.mp4?t=1768213542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >添加到您的愿望清单:   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了在开发过程中支持我们，请将我们的游戏添加到您的愿望清单，并加入我们的Discord！<br> </p>",
